WEBVTT

00:00:19.880 --> 00:00:25.400
Sahasrara Puja – “The Ghost of Materialism” 3rd May 1987

00:00:25.520 --> 00:00:26.760
Thredbo, Australia

00:00:31.640 --> 00:00:38.400
Today is a very great day for all the Sahaja yogis.

00:00:42.760 --> 00:00:53.000
It was a long time back that I desired

00:00:58.800 --> 00:01:06.240
Sahasrara should be opened out, but waiting for a right time.

00:01:06.360 --> 00:01:22.360
It was important to do it at the right time.

00:01:22.480 --> 00:01:34.760
A boy in Aurangabad, quite young, asked Me a question, “Mother, this all-pervading

00:01:34.880 --> 00:01:49.800
Power of Brahmachaitanya is beyond senses, you cannot feel it through senses.

00:01:49.920 --> 00:01:57.880
How is it we are now feeling it through our senses?”

00:01:58.000 --> 00:02:04.360
This is the question he asked, and I ask you the same question.

00:02:04.480 --> 00:02:19.880
Before this, those people who got realization could not talk about it in the way you can

00:02:20.000 --> 00:02:24.640
tell people, that you can feel it on your senses.

00:02:24.760 --> 00:02:34.200
They could not explain, they could not put it into experience.

00:02:34.320 --> 00:02:52.040
Just what they did was to tell them in words, words which were telling about something – like

00:02:52.160 --> 00:02:59.240
the taste of mango, unless and until you eat the mango how will you know the taste?

00:02:59.360 --> 00:03:04.160
By just knowing about “it’s wonderful, it’s great, it’s fantastic,” still you

00:03:04.280 --> 00:03:11.360
have not tasted the mango.

00:03:11.480 --> 00:03:17.480
So what has happened now, was the question.

00:03:17.600 --> 00:03:22.640
Another thing was that these people got so fed up, like Gyaneshwara at the age of twenty-one,

00:03:22.760 --> 00:03:26.040
he took a samadhi.

00:03:26.160 --> 00:03:34.720
He went into a room and closed the doors and settled down there, and he died there.

00:03:34.840 --> 00:03:40.400
All of them – even Christ got Himself crucified.

00:03:40.520 --> 00:03:51.840
Because they could tell a parable, they could tell a simile, but what had happened to them

00:03:51.960 --> 00:04:04.920
that they could not explain, and they felt so sad and so frustrated.

00:04:05.040 --> 00:04:09.760
In a way they finished their life very early.

00:04:09.880 --> 00:04:21.320
This was the question.

00:04:21.440 --> 00:04:27.960
So what was the secret, can any one of you tell Me?

00:04:56.280 --> 00:05:08.920
The answer is simple, but it’s difficult to digest.

00:05:11.680 --> 00:05:27.320
The answer is that all these incarnations who came on this Earth were part of the Sahasrara,

00:05:29.480 --> 00:05:35.240
were part of the Brahmachaitanya, were part of the Adi Shakti.

00:05:39.120 --> 00:05:48.280
They came on this Earth, gave realization to some people who were excellent, good people

00:05:48.520 --> 00:05:54.800
who had no problems; as if they came out of the ocean of love

00:05:54.920 --> 00:06:00.440
and took all of them to the ocean of love, to enjoy that ocean.

00:06:00.600 --> 00:06:06.160
As Kabira has said that “When a drop becomes the ocean, what can I say?”

00:06:06.680 --> 00:06:09.760
(“Jub mast hue, phir kya bole?”)

00:06:14.000 --> 00:06:18.800
So many of them took to mauna, that is silence.

00:06:18.920 --> 00:06:26.800
They disappeared, they got dissolved completely into the ocean of love.

00:06:29.280 --> 00:06:34.840
But you did not get dissolved.

00:06:37.480 --> 00:06:49.800
Something special has happened to you, that the whole of Brahmachaitanya, the whole ocean

00:06:50.200 --> 00:07:06.680
has taken the form of a cloud – that’s Adi Shakti – and has come on this Earth

00:07:06.800 --> 00:07:15.560
to shower the chaitanya on you people,

00:07:15.680 --> 00:07:23.560
enrich you, nurture you, develop you,

00:07:23.680 --> 00:07:39.720
by manifesting the love in such a manner that you have entered into the body of the Adi Shakti.

00:07:39.840 --> 00:07:48.600
So like one pitcher which is in the River Ganges, you are like a cell in the body of
the Adi Shakti.

00:07:48.720 --> 00:07:54.320
Your entity, your personality is preserved.

00:07:54.440 --> 00:08:02.760
Despite that you feel the Brahmachaitanya through your senses

00:08:02.880 --> 00:08:05.600
and you can give realizations
to others,

00:08:05.720 --> 00:08:09.080
but you are in the body of the Adi Shakti.

00:08:09.200 --> 00:08:18.440
As long as you are in the body of Adi Shakti you can do all that.

00:08:18.560 --> 00:08:21.240
This is the greatest thing that has happened.

00:08:21.360 --> 00:08:26.400
The whole of the Sahasrara has opened out with all the seven peethas

00:08:26.520 --> 00:08:31.080
of all the deities,
who are just part and parcel of it.

00:08:31.200 --> 00:08:43.280
The whole of it has come in the form of a Mother who is humble, who is deceptive, illusive,

00:08:43.400 --> 00:08:46.400
who is Mahamaya.

00:08:50.000 --> 00:08:56.880
It’s the greatest thing that could happen to human beings and to the whole universe,

00:08:57.000 --> 00:09:04.240
that now you can get your realization, you can give realizations to others,

00:09:04.360 --> 00:09:13.520
you can understand through your senses, through your logic what is vibrations, what it does.

00:09:14.240 --> 00:09:22.640
Just like the proof is here: all the flowers were dead last night,

00:09:22.760 --> 00:09:27.200
finished with the heat of the people who were carrying them.

00:09:27.320 --> 00:09:33.880
And then I just put some vibrated water on them, and you see how they are.

00:09:34.000 --> 00:09:42.560
Brahmachaitanya has revived them, but their personality is there, they are all vibrated,

00:09:42.680 --> 00:09:47.600
and they are looking so fresh and beautiful.

00:09:48.920 --> 00:09:53.480
Same thing with you, you all look so fresh and beautiful,

00:09:53.600 --> 00:09:57.560
anybody can make out a Sahaja yogi.

00:09:57.560 --> 00:10:01.800
Under these circumstances one has to understand

00:10:01.920 --> 00:10:05.560
that there are certain limitations which you have to observe.

00:10:05.680 --> 00:10:10.560
First of all, I have taken you in My body.

00:10:10.680 --> 00:10:19.400
A foreign thing has to go in the body and it has to be looked after, nurtured.

00:10:20.800 --> 00:10:30.480
But if you become troublesome, then you’ll be thrown out, I can’t bear you.

00:10:31.960 --> 00:10:36.440
Some people are extremely troublesome.

00:10:36.560 --> 00:10:45.400
They do not meditate, they have their own ideas about meditation,

00:10:45.520 --> 00:10:51.280
they do not develop themselves, they do not mature,

00:10:51.400 --> 00:10:56.760
they live in the past or in the future,

00:10:57.960 --> 00:11:00.800
and such people
are troublesome.

00:11:00.920 --> 00:11:06.840
A simple thing I’d requested you all, to put some ghee in the nose,

00:11:07.080 --> 00:11:10.600
which is a very
simple thing but is very important.

00:11:10.720 --> 00:11:20.800
You all suffer from a very bad Hamsa, and one of the things that is a symptom

00:11:20.920 --> 00:11:25.880
in a AIDS case is a bad Hamsa.

00:11:26.520 --> 00:11:35.960
You’ll be vulnerable to AIDS – and a small thing like that is not observed.

00:11:38.360 --> 00:11:47.760
It has to be a religious obligation that you must listen to Me, whatever I say.

00:11:47.880 --> 00:11:50.720
Actually you must obey Me.

00:11:50.840 --> 00:11:55.960
My hand obeys Me, My fingers obey Me, My feet obey Me;

00:11:56.080 --> 00:12:02.280
what about you, who are raised to the great dignity

00:12:02.400 --> 00:12:16.480
and the great position of being the yogis in the body of the Adi Shakti,

00:12:16.600 --> 00:12:24.000
and they are acting as cells in My body?

00:12:30.960 --> 00:12:38.240
First and foremost thing is, to do this kind of a venture,

00:12:38.360 --> 00:12:50.840
to put all kinds of things in your body is a very daring thing,

00:12:52.200 --> 00:12:57.280
and the process is also very hazardous.

00:13:00.360 --> 00:13:12.160
This has to be achieved with great patience, love, compassion and above all, hard labor.

00:13:17.040 --> 00:13:26.200
This has to be regarded as the greatest thing, that Sahasrara was opened by Me.

00:13:26.920 --> 00:13:35.760
Of course I am the master of Sahasrara, I am the master of all the chakras,

00:13:35.880 --> 00:13:42.160
but also I’m beyond Sahasrara, much beyond it.

00:13:42.280 --> 00:13:48.880
If that is the situation, you should be careful about your Sahasrara – that is Me –

00:13:49.000 --> 00:13:54.720
and looking after your own heart

00:13:54.840 --> 00:13:57.560
which is the Brahmarandra peetha here,

00:13:57.680 --> 00:14:02.640
which opens out ultimately when you get your realization.

00:14:03.800 --> 00:14:11.680
Sahaja Yoga is spreading everywhere horizontally; vertically it must also spread.

00:14:11.800 --> 00:14:18.360
And there, if you really have proper understanding of what I am,

00:14:18.480 --> 00:14:21.440
Sahasrara should be absolutely clearcut.

00:14:21.560 --> 00:14:26.440
And to keep Sahasrara clearcut you must listen to whatever I have told you,

00:14:26.560 --> 00:14:34.480
obey it as absolutely a ordained thing.

00:14:39.280 --> 00:14:43.880
To keep the Sahasrara clean is to open your heart.

00:14:44.000 --> 00:14:50.920
If your hearts are not open, how will I fill it up with My love?

00:14:51.040 --> 00:14:57.960
Open your heart to your fellow yogis and yoginis.

00:14:58.080 --> 00:15:01.720
Don’t get worried about what has happened in the past,

00:15:01.840 --> 00:15:06.640
don’t get worried about what has happened in your life

00:15:06.760 --> 00:15:11.840
as far as your relationships are concerned.

00:15:11.960 --> 00:15:19.160
Such things won’t happen now in Sahaja Yoga, they cannot happen.

00:15:19.280 --> 00:15:22.880
It has been worked out that way, it cannot happen.

00:15:23.000 --> 00:15:28.320
If this hand is paining, the other hand is there to help it out.

00:15:28.440 --> 00:15:35.520
You’re not alone, you are in the body of the collective being.

00:15:35.640 --> 00:15:40.600
If there are stupid people, if there are idiotic people,

00:15:40.720 --> 00:15:45.640
Sahaja Yoga is not meant for such people.

00:15:45.960 --> 00:15:48.920
In Sanskrit language they are called as “mudhahs.”

00:15:49.040 --> 00:15:56.640
Neither this is meant for people who are over-smart and trying to cheat themselves

00:15:56.760 --> 00:16:07.040
– intelligence has that capacity – and to indulge into things which are not Sahaj.

00:16:09.520 --> 00:16:13.080
Slowly you will find your vibrations will disappear,

00:16:13.200 --> 00:16:21.880
you’ll become sick, you’ll have problems and you’ll be in trouble.

00:16:22.000 --> 00:16:28.720
This is not a kind of a warning but a request, because you are in My body,

00:16:28.840 --> 00:16:44.480
and whenever anybody tries to be troublesome in My body I have to bear it up, and suffer a lot.

00:16:46.880 --> 00:16:52.720
It’s a funny type of a crucifixion when every moment

00:16:52.840 --> 00:16:59.520
you are hanged onto a cross by anyone who wants to do it.

00:17:03.640 --> 00:17:10.680
Sahaja yogis have all the laws in their hands to torture My life, to trouble Me

00:17:10.800 --> 00:17:21.160
if they want to; but they have also such a capacity, such a caliber,

00:17:21.280 --> 00:17:27.400
such a potential that they can reside in My heart forever.

00:17:28.000 --> 00:17:34.160
Open your hearts, that’s the thing I will say.

00:17:34.440 --> 00:17:39.760
Now we have to see what keeps our hearts closed.

00:17:39.880 --> 00:17:49.600
Firstly it keeps our heart in a binding, the fear of the past.

00:17:49.720 --> 00:17:55.080
In the past if you have done anything wrong, in the past

00:17:55.200 --> 00:18:02.240
we have had bad experiences of
people, we are very frightened.

00:18:02.400 --> 00:18:09.400
I’ve seen, I’m surprised, I’ve seen it Myself that in England

00:18:09.520 --> 00:18:15.800
when we were staying – it was that day unluckily or luckily

00:18:15.920 --> 00:18:22.720
it was snowing for the first time, and we were shifting, so I had gone out.

00:18:22.840 --> 00:18:28.320
And when I came back I saw a lady and a little baby in a pram,

00:18:28.440 --> 00:18:32.960
standing at the door and talking
to some lady.

00:18:33.080 --> 00:18:38.440
The other lady was just talking through a little opening

00:18:38.560 --> 00:18:43.000
in the door, because there
was a chain on.

00:18:43.120 --> 00:18:49.640
Then I went out and came back after half-an-hour, and I saw the same thing.

00:18:49.760 --> 00:18:55.800
The lady was still standing in the snow, and this lady was talking to her through a chink.

00:18:55.920 --> 00:18:58.280
I was surprised.

00:18:58.400 --> 00:19:01.920
What is this going like “Midsummer’s Night’s Dream,”

00:19:02.040 --> 00:19:06.840
these people are talking to each other – horrible!

00:19:06.960 --> 00:19:12.080
What was it that was frightening to this lady inside the room,

00:19:12.200 --> 00:19:16.200
what this lady would have done with the child, who had come to her door?

00:19:16.320 --> 00:19:19.560
What was there to be so frightened of?

00:19:19.680 --> 00:19:27.320
Because of the ego within yourself: you have frightened others, you have tortured others,

00:19:27.440 --> 00:19:33.080
you have dominated others, you have done all these things,

00:19:33.200 --> 00:19:39.440
so there is fear in your mind that others may do the same thing to you.

00:19:39.600 --> 00:19:42.360
Or what is there to be so much frightened,

00:19:42.480 --> 00:19:47.280
to lock your doors to everyone who comes to
your house?

00:19:51.000 --> 00:19:56.560
Secondly, maybe you might have been tortured by someone or troubled by someone,

00:19:56.680 --> 00:20:01.200
so your heart is closed, you can’t open heart to others.

00:20:01.320 --> 00:20:04.960
People just don’t talk, they just keep “mum.”

00:20:05.080 --> 00:20:06.920
What has happened?

00:20:07.040 --> 00:20:11.200
Just like a dead body moving about.

00:20:11.720 --> 00:20:21.720
Supposing I was like this, who would have told you the secrets of Sahaja Yoga and Sahasrara?

00:20:21.880 --> 00:20:28.160
So this kind of a nature comes from people who are frightened in the past perhaps,

00:20:28.280 --> 00:20:34.000
or they might have frightened people with their bad Vishuddhi.

00:20:35.760 --> 00:20:45.120
Aggressiveness is one of the qualities in the West, and that also is inherited by you
people.

00:20:45.240 --> 00:20:51.200
As soon as you put them onto something, they become aggressive.

00:20:51.320 --> 00:20:53.920
I can’t bear it within Myself.

00:20:54.040 --> 00:21:02.480
Supposing I have some sort of a medicine that makes some cells very aggressive,

00:21:02.600 --> 00:21:08.480
then what happens? Ultimately I become a patient of cancer.

00:21:10.160 --> 00:21:18.280
An aggressive cell is called as the malignant cell,

00:21:18.400 --> 00:21:24.320
and such a cell cannot give you proper attention, cannot give you proper depth,

00:21:24.440 --> 00:21:28.720
but you become nothing but a malignant cell,

00:21:28.840 --> 00:21:32.560
a cell which is creating a cancer.

00:21:32.680 --> 00:21:37.760
And such a person creates cancer among Sahaja yogis.

00:21:39.480 --> 00:21:47.080
I’ve heard horrible stories about how some women, some men have become aggressive.

00:21:47.200 --> 00:21:52.000
With a little position they get, immediately they become aggressive.

00:21:52.120 --> 00:21:59.560
Say somebody is a wife of a organizer, or a so-called leader’s,

00:21:59.680 --> 00:22:07.080
then she thinks she is nothing but a prime minister or something

00:22:07.200 --> 00:22:09.960
– or her husband becomes something.

00:22:10.080 --> 00:22:15.520
This aggressiveness adds to the aggressiveness of another person.

00:22:15.640 --> 00:22:17.720
So then reaction starts.

00:22:17.840 --> 00:22:22.720
One says something, the another says something; we become reactionaries.

00:22:22.840 --> 00:22:28.600
We haven’t got something of our own, that we should be reactionaries?

00:22:28.720 --> 00:22:32.080
There should be no reaction to anything,

00:22:33.240 --> 00:22:35.440
because we have something of our own.

00:22:35.560 --> 00:22:40.480
Why should we react to something, whatever people are doing to us or have done to us?

00:22:40.600 --> 00:22:42.800
– it’s finished.

00:22:44.040 --> 00:22:46.600
Open your hearts.

00:22:46.720 --> 00:22:52.560
That’s why when you came to India, I think you must have noticed that in the Indian heart

00:22:52.680 --> 00:23:00.800
there is nothing like an anger for say, for English or for Portuguese,

00:23:00.920 --> 00:23:05.480
or for anybody
who has dominated them.

00:23:05.600 --> 00:23:09.080
They have so much love and affection and respect,

00:23:09.200 --> 00:23:12.640
and they see that what good you have done
to them.

00:23:12.760 --> 00:23:18.560
Like some barristers came to India and they visited some high courts,

00:23:18.680 --> 00:23:22.480
and they had holiday for one day to celebrate

00:23:22.600 --> 00:23:29.680
the visit of these British lawyers and barristers.

00:23:31.800 --> 00:23:38.080
But if you go to England they will beat you, throw you out.

00:23:40.320 --> 00:23:47.120
This aggressiveness has to go from your heart, it has to get out of it.

00:23:47.240 --> 00:23:53.360
There’s no place in My body for aggressive people, no place at all.

00:23:55.600 --> 00:24:01.760
I have not aggressed you, and you shouldn’t aggress Me.

00:24:03.960 --> 00:24:08.320
If you aggress any Sahaja yogi, you are aggressing Me.

00:24:08.440 --> 00:24:12.960
But when it comes to others, they won’t aggress others.

00:24:13.080 --> 00:24:20.280
Like a bad husband will aggress his wife, but not other people.

00:24:20.400 --> 00:24:25.200
So those who are non-Sahaja yogis, they do not aggress them.

00:24:25.320 --> 00:24:33.080
That’s a very important part of Sahasrara, because ego covers a great part of Sahasrara,

00:24:33.240 --> 00:24:39.760
and if your Sahasrara is covered with this ego business,

00:24:39.880 --> 00:24:43.520
how can I help you and how can I help Myself?

00:24:43.640 --> 00:24:49.800
Now so many of you are in My body, just imagine, circulating fast;

00:24:49.920 --> 00:24:56.520
and most of them are fighting

00:24:57.080 --> 00:25:01.920
to be in My heart, but they are settling in My ego.

00:25:02.040 --> 00:25:09.840
Well, I am egoless, because I have no reactions.

00:25:09.960 --> 00:25:13.640
If you have no reaction you cannot develop ego.

00:25:13.760 --> 00:25:19.480
I’ve no reactions, I’m reactionless.

00:25:20.040 --> 00:25:33.560
I am in My own peace and glory, trying to work out Sahaja Yoga.

00:25:34.920 --> 00:25:47.080
I do not react to anything, but your reactions trouble Me because you are within Me.

00:25:47.200 --> 00:25:53.960
Then the second part is the fear that comes from childhood.

00:25:54.080 --> 00:26:01.160
I do not know about Americans, but so many Americans who came to Me

00:26:01.280 --> 00:26:06.560
were half-mad, cracked people, absolutely cracked in the head,

