00:28:05.200 --> 00:28:13.000
You can’t find Americans when they are talking, any good speaker,

00:28:13.120 --> 00:28:18.280
who doesn’t have twitches on his faces, on his body, everywhere,

00:28:18.400 --> 00:28:24.080
because so many nerves have been already strained

00:28:27.600 --> 00:28:32.720
with this kind of “what’s wrong?” business.

00:28:32.840 --> 00:28:37.200
Going to the other extreme of deciding everything for yourself.

00:28:37.320 --> 00:28:50.800
And the thing behind is a ghost, I should say, a very big ghost,

00:28:50.920 --> 00:28:55.800
and which is not in the past or the future, but in the present.

00:28:55.920 --> 00:28:59.280
And that ghost I call it as materialism.

00:28:59.400 --> 00:29:05.800
Materialism – it’s a ghost, it’s a horrible devil

00:29:05.920 --> 00:29:15.280
that has come onto the heads of Americans, and from them to all of us.

00:29:15.400 --> 00:29:21.360
This materialism is a horrible stuff.

00:29:21.480 --> 00:29:33.120
It’s so ridiculous, shameful, doesn’t even suit a human person; even a dog

00:29:33.240 --> 00:29:41.000
would hate such a materialism, to what level human beings have gone.

00:29:45.680 --> 00:29:52.040
This materialism makes a person absolutely shameless.

