A lady would not mind asking another lady:

00:30:00.120 --> 00:30:05.320
“By the way, have you got my spoons with
you?”

00:30:05.440 --> 00:30:07.480
There’s no shame in it.

00:30:11.520 --> 00:30:17.800
When we were small we were told in India – I mean, that’s our culture –

00:30:17.920 --> 00:30:24.960
that if somebody’s pin is in your house you should preserve it and return it,

00:30:25.120 --> 00:30:29.800
but even if your diamond is lost with somebody, never ask for it.

00:30:29.920 --> 00:30:33.760
Is not good manners.

00:30:35.200 --> 00:30:43.000
What is more valuable is not the diamond, is the relationship,

00:30:43.120 --> 00:30:50.240
is the friendship, and the emotions of human beings to be respected.

00:30:50.360 --> 00:30:52.240
How can you ask?

00:30:52.360 --> 00:30:56.480
If there was a diamond they would have found it and would have given it to you,

00:30:56.600 --> 00:31:01.760
but if there is no asking for that or reporting like that

00:31:01.880 --> 00:31:05.560
then it’s sure there’s no diamond; and even if it is there, doesn’t matter.

00:31:05.680 --> 00:31:12.760
After all, what is a diamond? – you are wearing or they are wearing, what does it
matter?

00:31:14.960 --> 00:31:22.680
In My father’s house all the doors were open all the time, all the doors, day and
night.

00:31:22.840 --> 00:31:27.240
Never a thief came in, thought that doors are open so nothing is locked,

00:31:27.360 --> 00:31:30.200
there’s nothing precious.

00:31:30.320 --> 00:31:33.760
Only we had one theft, and the thief came

00:31:33.880 --> 00:31:38.520
and took away a gramophone from us, and some
records.

00:31:38.640 --> 00:31:41.480
So My father said, “He’s a connoisseur.

00:31:41.600 --> 00:31:44.920
He took the right thing from this house, so let it be.

00:31:45.040 --> 00:31:48.120
What’s the use of informing the police?”

00:31:52.960 --> 00:32:02.200
So this materialism that comes in is a mad, mad, mad dog,

00:32:02.320 --> 00:32:10.000
and gives you a disease which is worse than any disease that is possible.

00:32:10.120 --> 00:32:18.200
How people play on it, on this disease, as you must have known that doctors

00:32:18.320 --> 00:32:21.280
when you
get some disease little bit, t

00:32:21.400 --> 00:32:25.760
hey’ll take out your teeth, take out your eyes, take out your nose, take out

00:32:25.880 --> 00:32:28.880
your purse and take out everything that you have,

00:32:29.000 --> 00:32:32.840
for a little thing like malaria or something.

00:32:32.960 --> 00:32:40.480
But this disease takes away everything that is beautiful within you,

00:32:40.600 --> 00:32:43.720
that is good within
you.

00:32:43.840 --> 00:32:47.480
For example, it started a fashion.

00:32:47.600 --> 00:32:51.520
With this materialism they start fashions.

00:32:51.640 --> 00:32:54.600
Ladies are more vulnerable.

00:32:54.760 --> 00:33:01.760
Fashion starts, any sort of fashion starts, like the sleeves to be made long,

00:33:01.880 --> 00:33:05.040
in India also they started – then make it short,

00:33:05.160 --> 00:33:08.840
then make it half, then make it no sleeves.

00:33:08.960 --> 00:33:11.720
I said, “I am not running that race.

00:33:11.840 --> 00:33:17.320
I will have the sleeves all the time, same sleeves so I don’t have to bother.

00:33:17.440 --> 00:33:21.600
I can tell My tailor and he can make whatever way I want to have,

00:33:21.720 --> 00:33:27.720
the tailor, because he knows I make one style” – finished with it.

00:33:27.840 --> 00:33:31.000
Why do people want to run with the fashion?

00:33:31.120 --> 00:33:37.760
Just think of it, what is the need to run with the fashion?

00:33:37.880 --> 00:33:40.840
Now new race has started, run with it.

00:33:40.960 --> 00:33:45.880
Then another race has started, run with it.
Then the third race has started, run with it.

00:33:46.000 --> 00:33:52.040
All the time running with the mad race of fashions.

00:33:53.280 --> 00:33:59.600
Now a new race has started of fashions not to put any oil in the head,

00:33:59.720 --> 00:34:04.000
so you become
bald, then you buy wigs.

00:34:04.120 --> 00:34:09.000
It’s all entrepreneurs who are working out, it’s all enterprises.

00:34:09.120 --> 00:34:20.400
So you become absolutely bald-headed people, then you get your wigs from them,

00:34:20.520 --> 00:34:26.640
then there
is a special charge for dressing the wigs, so you go for dressing the wigs.

00:34:26.760 --> 00:34:29.680
Goes on like mad.

00:34:30.880 --> 00:34:38.120
Then there’s another type: now a new fashion has started in London

00:34:38.240 --> 00:34:43.200
because, you see, these
people want to make some money.

