People don’t even have so much of logic and intelligence left in their heads

00:34:47.920 --> 00:34:53.040
to see
that what they were preaching one day, they are just the thing against it.

00:34:53.160 --> 00:35:00.120
Formerly it was you had to wear a tail coat, you had to have your hair absolutely done

00:35:00.240 --> 00:35:07.200
with proper hair-grooming and all that, as you can see in the old pictures.

00:35:07.320 --> 00:35:12.760
Then it started striped three-piece suits.

00:35:12.880 --> 00:35:19.040
Now it is, I mean, few days earlier was tight clothes,

00:35:19.160 --> 00:35:22.160
then they developed varicose veins, you see.

00:35:22.280 --> 00:35:27.800
So no, no – now it is the fashion to wear absolutely loose dresses.

00:35:27.960 --> 00:35:34.760
I saw the other day one lady making a dress out of a big blanket, going like this.

00:35:34.960 --> 00:35:39.680
I thought she was some priest or someone!

00:35:42.080 --> 00:35:45.280
So that stupidity has started.

00:35:45.400 --> 00:35:54.560
Imagine – think of Sahasrara, think of Divine, in what world we are,

00:35:54.680 --> 00:35:59.080
and in what world the stupid people are going.

00:35:59.200 --> 00:36:04.720
That’s another world, absolutely another stupid world

00:36:04.840 --> 00:36:08.640
where people just go after nonsensical things,

00:36:08.760 --> 00:36:12.680
changing from one to another, changing from everything:

00:36:12.800 --> 00:36:16.000
ties are changed, everything
is changed, giving you such a headache.

00:36:16.120 --> 00:36:19.240
All the time you have to think, “Now what fashion is there?

00:36:19.360 --> 00:36:21.280
Let’s find out in the newspaper.

00:36:21.400 --> 00:36:25.560
What is – this is the fashion now. All right, wear this dress.”

00:36:25.680 --> 00:36:32.560
All this is befooling going on, because this ghost has entered into us.

00:36:32.680 --> 00:36:36.840
In Sahaja Yoga also when we enter, be careful,

00:36:36.960 --> 00:36:42.400
materialism should not enter into your minds.

00:36:43.320 --> 00:36:47.560
It’s nothing important.

00:36:47.680 --> 00:36:52.440
Even when somebody dies you are supposed to wear something black,

00:36:52.560 --> 00:36:56.280
or white or I don’t
know what else, but white or black.

00:36:56.400 --> 00:37:02.200
And somebody died in England who was a great friend of My husband,

00:37:02.320 --> 00:37:05.400
and I had no black sari, completely black.

00:37:05.520 --> 00:37:08.920
I mean we don’t have such a sari.
