00:37:13.000 --> 00:37:20.000
Imagine how his wife would feel if I don’t go to the thing, how she would take it.

00:37:20.120 --> 00:37:25.760
All this is nothing, what is important is the black sari!

00:37:25.880 --> 00:37:33.560
In every walk of life you are being befooled by this materialism.

00:37:33.680 --> 00:37:39.400
I don’t know how you got stuck into it first of all.

00:37:39.520 --> 00:37:42.920
And the other side is, the same people are befooling you.

00:37:43.040 --> 00:37:48.400
“All right, this is not good, this is too much” – so go to the anti-culture.

00:37:48.520 --> 00:37:55.520
What is anti-culture is another kind of materialism, another kind of nonsense.

00:37:55.640 --> 00:38:00.000
Nowadays they are having in this London an anti-culture movement

00:38:00.120 --> 00:38:02.240
which is called as “punks.”

00:38:02.360 --> 00:38:08.560
I think out of date now Me, but still what’s for the time being as I see is punks.

00:38:08.680 --> 00:38:11.960
It costs them forty pounds sometimes to make that hair.

00:38:12.080 --> 00:38:19.040
I mean, is it something that you are saving money on that?

00:38:20.120 --> 00:38:26.840
So the whole thing works out just to take out your attention from reality,

00:38:26.960 --> 00:38:33.560
from higher
values, to something nonsensical.

00:38:35.880 --> 00:38:44.520
In Sahaja Yoga also people must learn to lead a life of collectivity.

00:38:44.640 --> 00:38:51.760
It’s very important that we have to be collective.

00:38:51.880 --> 00:38:57.920
We shouldn’t talk of “This is mine, this is mine, and this I own.”

00:38:58.040 --> 00:39:03.160
Even about children you should not do like that, “This is my own child, this is my

