own baby.

00:39:04.480 --> 00:39:12.760
This is my brother, this is my sister.”

00:39:12.880 --> 00:39:18.280
This “my, my” should go away; but that’s not possible, it’s not easy to forget about

00:39:18.400 --> 00:39:23.880
it because left Nabhi and right Nabhi has to be all right.

00:39:24.000 --> 00:39:30.120
The only way to do it is that “Mother, it’s all Yours.”

00:39:30.240 --> 00:39:36.480
It’s not dangerous to say that, because I’ll never take anything that is supposed

00:39:36.600 --> 00:39:40.320
to be yours.

00:39:40.440 --> 00:39:45.040
Just to say, “Mother, it’s all Yours,” to start it – “It’s all Yours.

00:39:45.160 --> 00:39:53.080
I am Yours, my heart is Yours, all my things are Yours, my life is Yours.”

00:39:53.200 --> 00:39:58.200
Even saying that is a big mantra for Sahasrara.

00:39:58.320 --> 00:40:07.280
The deity of Sahasrara is a very simple person, extremely simple, and can be moved with very

00:40:07.400 --> 00:40:12.960
little actions, can be pleased with very few little actions here and there.

00:40:13.120 --> 00:40:16.480
Not much is needed to please the deity of Sahasrara.

00:40:16.600 --> 00:40:26.800
It’s a very simple person; little things make Her happy.

00:40:26.920 --> 00:40:32.480
Yesterday you had brought the flowers, and I didn’t take them.

00:40:32.600 --> 00:40:36.240
You all must have thought, “What’s it, we couldn’t give flowers to Mother, holding

00:40:36.360 --> 00:40:37.360
in our hand.”

