But I wanted to show this miracle to you, that’s why I didn’t take.

00:40:42.680 --> 00:40:48.440
And I took it in the end, and see now they are the best among all of them; don’t they

00:40:48.560 --> 00:40:54.360
look as if they have been plucked from the tree?

00:40:54.480 --> 00:41:00.480
Just I wanted to show this, so I said, “I’m tired,” I sat down and then I looked at

00:41:00.600 --> 00:41:08.840
you with the flowers, you see, in the hands, you’re sitting all of you!

00:41:08.960 --> 00:41:18.440
So She is Leela Vinodini.

00:41:18.560 --> 00:41:26.960
She plays around, makes little mischiefs here and there for you to learn lessons.

00:41:27.120 --> 00:41:33.640
Because if I tell you “Do this” then it’s not possible, but little circuitous way I

00:41:33.760 --> 00:41:37.360
can show you that this is wrong, you should not do it.

