I don’t know if you thought of it or not, but I knew it Myself that I have to take the

00:41:55.320 --> 00:42:00.640
flowers to show this miracle to them, that these flowers are going to last much longer

00:42:00.760 --> 00:42:08.040
than any other flowers, because they are vibrated with the Brahmachaitanya.

00:42:08.160 --> 00:42:13.080
And the water was very, very, very cold, so even I opened a hot water tap.

00:42:13.200 --> 00:42:21.960
It’s all right, doesn’t matter, they didn’t die, despite that they are perfectly all right.

